    <text>
        <body>
            <div type="edition">
                <div type="textpart">
                    <ab>(S) In Christi nomine. Breve recordationis ad memoria habendam vel
                        retinendam inpositum, qualiter actum est in <rs key="#Castle">castro</rs> de
                            <placeName key="#Castle" ref="#places/3229">Grofolesco</placeName>,
                        presentia <rs key="#Boni_viri/boni_homines">bonorum hominum</rs> quorum
                        nomina inferius scripta ponuntur. Filii quondam <persName><name
                                ref="Robertus">Ruberti</name></persName>, <persName><name
                                ref="Herimanni">Armannus</name></persName> magister et
                                <persName><name ref="Garimundus">Guermondellus</name></persName> et
                        uxor eius <persName><name ref="Bonamica">Bonamica</name></persName> et
                                <persName><name ref="Lupinus">Lupinus</name></persName> et uxor eius
                                <persName><name ref="Imilda">Imelda</name></persName> et
                                <persName><name ref="Zamparone">Zamparone</name></persName> et uxor
                        eius <persName><name ref="Gunthilda">Guntelda</name></persName> investierunt
                        et dederunt per tenimentum <persName><name ref="Albertus"
                            >Alberto</name></persName>, qui tunc erat rector <orgName
                            key="#Bridges/pontoons #Hospitals" ref="#juridical_persons/3209"><rs
                                key="#Hospitals">hospitalis</rs> de <rs key="#Bridges/pontoons"
                                >ponte</rs>
                            <placeName key="#Bridges/pontoons #Hospitals" ref="#places/3200"
                                >Ficeclensi</placeName></orgName> (pro amore et remedio animarum
                        suarum et suorum parentium) videlicet unum petium de terra quod est positum
                        a <placeName ref="#places/3215">Cerro Aquilaio</placeName>, terrefinatum
                        (sic) ab uno latere cum terra filiorum <persName><name ref="Truffa"
                                >Truffe</name></persName> et aliud caput cum <orgName
                            key="#Hospitals" ref="#juridical_persons/3203">hospitalis <placeName
                                key="#Forests #Hospitals" ref="#places/3215"
                            >Rosarie</placeName></orgName>
                        <rs key="#Forests">busco</rs>, et latus unus tenet in Giusciana, aliud latus
                        tenet in carraria veccla. (…) Tantum est ut per omne (annum) in <rs
                            key="#Periodic_markets">mercato</rs>
                        <placeName key="#Periodic_markets" ref="#places/3230">Pogiguisi</placeName>
                        pensionem exinde solvere debeat predictus Albertus et eius successores vel
                        missus ad predictos filios Ruberti (…) duos solidos bonorum denariorum et
                        non amplius. (…) <foreign>Pena</foreign>: bonorum denariorum sol. mille.
                        Servitium fecit Albertus rector hospitalis de ponte Ficeclensi ad
                        supranominatos filios Ruberti sol. XX. Hoc actum est presentia <persName
                            key="#Witness #Boni_viri/boni_homines"><name ref="Manno"
                            >Manni</name></persName> quondam <persName><name ref="Teudericus"
                                >Tederigi</name></persName> et <persName
                            key="#Witness #Boni_viri/boni_homines"><name ref="Lucterius"
                                >Locterii</name></persName> quondam <persName><name ref="Francus"
                                >Franci</name></persName> et <persName
                            key="#Witness #Boni_viri/boni_homines"><name ref="Garandus"
                                >Carandi</name></persName> quondam <persName><name ref="Folle"
                                >Folli</name></persName> et aliorum multorum <rs key="#Witness"
                            >testium</rs>. Anno ab incarnatione domini nostri Iehsu Christi
                        MCLXIIII, indictione II, idus septembris. (S) Ego <persName
                            key="#Writer #Notary"><name ref="Glottus">Glottus</name></persName>
                        <rs key="#Notary">notarius</rs> domni imperatoris hoc breve <rs
                            key="#Writer">scripsi</rs> et ibi fui. </ab>
                </div>
